Product description

Color:657 Nude Nuance

Discover Maybelline New Yorks Color Sensational Creamy Matte Lipsticks in 35 comfortably matte shades! Infused with pure precious oils that are filled with moisture; our smoothest, creamiest, non-drying matte lipstick leaves the lips with a sensuous finish for that comfortable feel. The Creamy Mattes are available in 35 stunning and highly pigmented shades; ranging from classic red lipsticks such as Rich Ruby and Siren in Scarlet to flawless nude lipsticks like Daringly Nude and Nude Embrace.

How does Amazon calculate star ratings?
Amazon calculates a product's star ratings based on a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The model takes into account factors including the age of a rating, whether the ratings are from verified purchasers and factors that establish reviewer trustworthiness.
